## Post status filter

Post status filter is used to filter posts by their WP post status e.g Published, Draft, Pending etc. These statuses must be [included in the index](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_post-type-filters-orders-and-indexing_.md) for this filter to work. It is typically used to create a front-end post management page, to let authors filter their posts by status.

Only post authors themselves can view their non published posts in front-end. As such, when using the Post Status filter, you also have to add [Author filter](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_author-filter_.md) and define a default value for it.
